  "title": "Assistant Key Account Manager | Supply Chain Solutions",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a market leaders in providing Supply Chain Solutions. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for an Assistant Key Account Manager to join their Key Account team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located at East.</strong></p><p>Duties of the Assistant Key Account Manager</p><p><ul><li>Drive revenue and margin growth across assigned customer accounts, delivering against EBIT and working capital targets.</li><li>Develop and execute strategic Key Account Plans to achieve short- and long-term commercial outcomes.</li><li>Own customer service agreements, ensuring contractual KPIs and cost-saving commitments are met or exceeded.</li><li>Oversee day-to-day account operations, including pricing accuracy and service delivery.</li><li>Lead margin improvement initiatives and act as a change agent for commercial optimisation.</li><li>Analyse performance data, conduct regular business reviews, and implement continuous improvements.</li><li>Identify and secure new growth opportunities within existing accounts.</li><li>Collaborate closely with internal teams to deliver best-in-class customer service.</li><li>Ensure full compliance with sales policies and procedures.</li><li>Foster a collaborative, high-performance culture internally and with customers.</li></ul></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Min Diploma in related field</li><li>Proven track record in key account management, by providing supply chain consultation</li><li>Understanding of financial concepts such as EBIT and working capital</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No. 19C9682<br />EA Reg. No. R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
